## Container Usage

```html
<!-- Responsive container -->
<div class="container mx-auto px-8 md:px-6 sm:px-4">
  <!-- Content scales with screen size -->
</div>

<!-- Max-width containers -->
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-8">  <!-- 1280px max -->
  <!-- Wide content -->
</div>

<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-8">  <!-- 896px max -->
  <!-- Article content -->
</div>

<div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-8">  <!-- 672px max -->
  <!-- Narrow content -->
</div>
```
